สำหรับ Core Events แบ่งออกเป็น

1. ***Message events:*** <br/> Messages are sent asynchronously 1 to 1 between pools:
	* Catching semantics – wait for a specified message from a different pool and then emit a token.
	* Throwing semantics – on receipt of a token, send a specified message to a different pool.

2. ***Signal events:***   <br/> Signals are broadcast asynchronously 1 to many within or between pools:
	* Catching semantics – wait for a specified signal then emit a token.
	* Throwing semantics – on receipt of a token, broadcast a specified signal.

3. ***Timer events:***   
	* When a time condition becomes True, emit a token.

4. ***Conditional events:***      
	* When a Boolean condition transitions from False to True (edge-triggered), emit a token.      

